# tsgo.patch
# pinned upstream SHA: 2bd066d87f5bafd315be9f40889d0a60b9e58e0b (tag typescript/v7.0.2 — TypeScript 7.0 GA)
# Applies on top of the submodule pinned in vendor/tsgo. Adds Yarn PnP module
# resolution (internal/pnp, internal/vfs/pnpvfs, resolver/modulespecifiers hooks)
# and the luchta-tsc-worker glue (internal/luchta, cmd/luchta-tsc-worker).
# regenerate: check out vendor/tsgo at the pinned SHA, apply this patch, resolve
#   any rejects, then: git -C vendor/tsgo add -A && \
#   git -C vendor/tsgo diff --binary --staged 2bd066d87f5bafd315be9f40889d0a60b9e58e0b > patches/tsgo.patch
# NOTE: always use --binary (CRLF preservation); .gitattributes keeps this file -text.
#   The Yarn PnP runtime fixtures (testdata/fixtures/pnp/*.cjs) are intentionally
#   included so the vendored pnp tests are self-contained.
